code_examples.code:
```
# Define a custom schema
from pydantic import BaseModel
class Data(BaseModel):
    data: str

# Create a FastAPI app with a route that accepts the Data schema
from fastapi import FastAPI
app = FastAPI()
@app.post('/my_route/')
def my_route(data: Data):
    return {'result': data.data}
``
